             <h2><img src="/bursar_office/images/The-university.jpg" width="590" height="393" alt="The-university" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; border: 2px double #000000;"></h2> 
             <hr> 
             <p><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">The Bursar of the University, appointed by the Board of Management, is responsible for the administration and the control of the University Funds and maintains relevant records.&nbsp;</span></p> 
             <h1 style="color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #333399;">Subject Areas handled by the Bursarâ€™s Office</span></span></h1> 
             <hr style="color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: center;"> 
             <ul style="color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: center;"> 
              <li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Making all payments including Salaries and allowances</span></li> 
              <li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Preparation of Annual Budget, Supplementary Budget and change of Vote Allocations</span></li> 
              <li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Collection of government grants and all generated income including course fees of fee-levying students and FGS students</span></li> 
              <li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Maintain votes ledgers, ledger accounts and other records</span></li> 
              <li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Maintain assets registers and pay records</span></li> 
              <li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Preparation of periodic Financial Statements and annual Financial Statements</span></li> 
              <li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Perform duties of procurement committees</span></li> 
              <li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Finalizing necessary financial information to the Board of Management</span></li> 
             </ul> 
             <hr> 
             <p>&nbsp;</p> 
